# Livewire Blade UI Standards

- Use existing Blade/Flux/Livewire patterns before adding JS.
- Prefer Tailwind utilities and native form/browser behavior over custom scripts.
- Keep Vietnamese UI copy consistent with surrounding views.
- Preserve accessibility: labels, focus states, keyboard access, and meaningful button text.
- For image UI, keep paths compatible with `AiImageEditor`, `AiImage::downloadName()`, and imgproxy volumes.
- Verify visible UI changes with `npm run build` in container when assets changed.
